pt or supporting evidence<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"heading h4\">Contact Information<\/h3>\n<p>You can submit your report via email to <a href=\"mailto:cybersecurity@panteracapital.com\">cybersecurity@panteracapital.com<\/a>\u00a0or use our submission form.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"heading h4\">Legal Terms<\/h3>\n<p>By participating in our bug bounty program, you agree to the following terms:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li>You must comply with all applicable laws and regulations.<\/li>\n<li>You must not violate the privacy of our users, destroy data, or interrupt our services.<\/li>\n<li>You must not exploit the vulnerability you discover for any reason other than testing and reporting it to us.<\/li>\n<li>We reserve the right to determine whether a vulnerability is eligible for a reward and the amount of the reward.<\/li>\n<li>We may modify the terms of this program or terminate it at any time without notice.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Welcome to our Bug Bounty Program. We appreciate your efforts in helping us improve our security. &nbsp; &nbsp; Scope Our bug bounty program covers the following areas: Web applications Mobile applications APIs Network infrastructure &nbsp; Rewards We offer rewards based on the severity of the vulnerability: Low severity: $100 &#8211; $500 Medium severity: $500 &#8211; [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"privacy-policy.php","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"content-type":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-9651","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v24.8.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Bug Bounty | Pantera<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<